article.headline: Barker, Troy east past Georgia State 37-20
article.description: Kaleb Barker was 9-of-10 passing for 136 yards and two touchdowns -- all in the first half -- and Troy cruised by Georgia State 37-20 on Thursday night to extend the nation's third-longest conference winning streak.
article.linkText: Barker, Troy east past Georgia State 37-20

images.name: Troy doubles lead with 50-yard TD pass
images.caption: QB Kaleb Barker launches one down the field, and hits WR Tray Eafford in stride to put the Trojans up 14-0.

video.headline: Troy doubles lead with 50-yard TD pass
video.caption: QB Kaleb Barker launches one down the field, and hits WR Tray Eafford in stride to put the Trojans up 14-0.
video.title: Troy doubles lead with 50-yard TD pass
video.description: QB Kaleb Barker launches one down the field, and hits WR Tray Eafford in stride to put the Trojans up 14-0.

article.story: TROY, Ala. -- Kaleb Barker was 9-of-10 passing for 136 yards and two touchdowns -- all in the first half -- and Troy cruised by Georgia State 37-20 on Thursday night to extend the nation's third-longest conference winning streak. Troy (5-1, 3-0 Sun Belt) has won nine straight leagues games, trailing UCF and Oklahoma. On the first play of the game, Barker scrambled for a 71-yard gain before being taken town at the 4. B.J. Smith capped the drive with a 2-yard touchdown run. Tyler Murray forced a fumble in the red zone on Georgia State's first possession, and the Trojans went 90 yards to take a 14-0 lead on Tray Eafford's 50-yard touchdown grab. Troy scored on its third straight drive as Barker connected with Deondre Douglas. Hunter Reese's sack and safety made it 23-0. Dan Ellington had 272 passing yards and 59 rushing for Georgia State (3-3, 1-1), which was outgained 350-123 in the first half. The Panthers scored both of their touchdowns in the final seven minutes.

videos.headline: 75-yard QB run sets up Troy's opening TD
videos.description: Kaleb Barker takes off down the sideline and gets all the way to the 4-yard line, setting up B.J. Smith's 2-yard touchdown run to make it 7-0 Trojans.

videos.headline: Barker throws strike for 2nd TD pass of game
videos.description: Kaleb Barker connects with WR Deondre Douglas for a 12-yard touchdown pass, extending Troy's lead to 21-0.

videos.headline: Troy WR drops easy TD and gifts Georgia State a takeaway
videos.description: Tray Eafford makes an inexcusable drop, and incidentally knocks the ball into the hands of a trailing Panthers DB.

videos.headline: Troy widens lead with 41-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB Sawyer Smith  drops a dime to WR Damion Willis, who dives for the pylon and makes it 30-6 Trojans.

videos.headline: Troy puts on finishing touches with 78-yard TD run
videos.description: RB B.J. Smith finds a seam and outruns the defense all the way to the end zone, making it 37-12 Trojans late in the 4th quarter.
